{"tid":501783,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲好哀怨嘅歌推薦","createTime":"2017-12-17T08:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T07:22:18.000Z","uid":49018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a53e45c53a2b586030fcb6e7ed96c524bc0128b4","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"而家自己聽緊夢到內河<br />\n有冇其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mvwGkldKD_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmvwGkldKD_Q&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8b426ae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mvwGkldKD_Q</a><br />\n<br />\n夢到內河<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：C.Y.Kong<br />\n演唱：張國榮<br />\n<br />\n你叫我這麼感動　但是這是我　你有可能戲弄<br />\n怎麼肯親手展示　如何被抱擁　我兩手還有用<br />\n你贈我一巴掌吧　為什麼未痛　我也許在發夢<br />\n當初的溫馨舉動　拿來做分手的慶功　令我精竭力窮<br />\n<br />\n自那日遺下我　我早化做燐火　湖泊上伴你這天鵝<br />\n但你為何還要　也許單手怕握不死我<br />\n若要死這一刻正是愉快高峰　請給我更多<br />\n<br />\n#(誰還)在內河上　我在內河上<br />\n望著沿岸高潮　快救活我溫暖我十秒　快將我怨念傳召<br />\n誰還在內河上　猶如做夢那樣　但奈何沒有天橋<br />\n跨不過這生彼岸　會將你壯麗忘掉　如果有這需要<br />\n<br />\n差不多不懂感動　就像死掉了　兩腳竟能震動<br />\n不應該這麼激動　仍然能夠哭　我眼睛還有用<br />\n拗轉我這雙手吧　但願這陣痛　說我不是發夢<br />\n你為何這麼衝動　拿流浪的軀體抱擁　直到精竭力窮<br />\n<br />\n自那日遺下我　我早化做燐火　湖泊上伴你這天鵝<br />\n但你為何還要　也許單手怕握不死我<br />\n若要死這一刻正是愉快高峰　請給我更多"},{"pid":"4f23aa4b1b2fb8d22de38ded21438c6063967ed2","tid":501783,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"愛慕"},{"pid":"d9fffd652cd378019f3d5a8d80518ab898528feb","tid":501783,"uid":154079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"睡前服<br />\n不如不見<br />\n單魚座"},{"pid":"84b8d7556870ef57f81595358e64abfe80140e7d","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛慕</blockquote><br />\n達到瘋癲程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcab24bdbd9a48d43811ffaabbcb0d4ddd6d3017","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睡前服<br />\n不如不見<br />\n單魚座</blockquote><br />\n即使再見面 成熟地表演<br />\n不如不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c33b4131514ea53c35dca5b2b8dc12c3873150f","tid":501783,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"陳百強：寂寞的感覺、漫長盼望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022b417a593fcc59385b923e45d9cd2534e723de","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳百強：寂寞的感覺、漫長盼望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n《等》尾聲嗰低吟我覺得係全首歌嘅精粹"},{"pid":"391731593dfc312f7ea569304a3c4d612c8ba409","tid":501783,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陳百強：寂寞的感覺、漫長盼望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n《等》尾聲嗰低吟我覺得係全首歌嘅精粹</blockquote><br />\n將前面積壓咗三分鐘嘅情感一次過爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d631bf1c35bfc1aeb9a08121cc3b728f656f7d36","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"其實張敬軒首《井》都好正<br />\n特別係經歷過識嘅人自殺<br />\n好無奈 好後悔<br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃偉文<br />\n呼吸一閉起 彷彿可以飛 飄上天際空氣<br />\n最後驀然回頭望這地 發現已死<br />\n怎麼苦戀到死 先想起轉機 不必這樣收尾<br />\n我要是為情能沉下去 便有勇氣一力 爬起<br />\n<br />\n芳心經已死 屍體不會飛 不要視為傳奇<br />\n要是墓前能留下見地 記著愛己<br />\n不應偏執到死 先清楚記起 根本這是歪理<br />\n你會為情人捱完毒氣 但你卻對生命 兒嬉"},{"pid":"a4a0bcf73d91026e68c0bc50ee543fcc5bc0811a","tid":501783,"uid":182558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"你又諷刺。。。"},{"pid":"01adc616828252205de2af660d21feab88a5b484","tid":501783,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a0bcf73d91026e68c0bc50ee543fcc5bc0811a","tid":501783,"uid":182558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"你又諷刺。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"我冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}